OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773601891
OL,3,CDozens of guns handed in during month-
OL,4,Clong amnesty
OL,6,FMore than 40 weapons were handed in to
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire Police during a month-
OL,8,Flong blank firing gun amnesty across
OL,9,Fthe county.
OL,11,FThe force joined a campaign throughout
OL,12,FFebruary to encourage owners of
OL,13,Fspecific models to hand them in after
OL,14,Ftests showed they were readily
OL,15,Fconvertible and therefore illegal.
OL,17,FPeople could hand in the guns at
OL,18,Fpolice stations across South Yorkshire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
