OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773601891
OL,3,CDozens of guns handed in during month-
OL,4,Clong amnesty
OL,6,FThe amnesty resulted in 22 Bruni blank
OL,7,Ffirearms being surrendered, as well as
OL,8,F23 other guns and 117 rounds of blank
OL,9,Fammunition.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Matthew Barnes, of
OL,12,Four Armed Crime Team, said: "Thank you
OL,13,Fto everyone who has helped make South
OL,14,FYorkshire a safer place by handing
OL,15,Fover these blank firers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
